<collectingCountry id="45BB760EC00BFF91FD17FE498983FE2F" box="[652,721,397,421]" name="Spain" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">Spain</collectingCountry>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3D13369EC00BFF91FF5EFE748A68FE67" blockId="10.[151,1436,289,566]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">
<emphasis id="0FD8EA8CC00BFF91FF5EFE748AE5FE43" bold="true" box="[197,439,432,457]" pageId="10" pageNumber="57">Relation to the host.</emphasis>
The mite is associated with leaf margin rolling, leaf lamina curling and abnormal hairiness of leaves.
</paragraph>
